channel.title: How do i make a silabsoft server?
channel.description: :confused: i want to actually MAKE one, not use someones source that is already created, but here's the thing, i have no clue about programming what so ever, plz help me! i don't get how to make one, do i have to have all of that coding? like client.java and compile.bat and that stuff? i am clueless, i just want to b on a server where i am the owner

item.title: How do i make a silabsoft server?
item.dc:creator: @Rog3r Rog3r
item.description:
@Rog3r wrote:

Get one from the download section, and edit it.

And to make yourself owner, first go on the server and then in the characters folder, select your profile and where it says: playerRights
Change from 0 to 3.

Read full topic
